00:01:56.020 --> 00:01:58.330
father, along with your half-sister

00:01:58.730 --> 00:02:00.020
from his first marriage.

00:02:00.750 --> 00:02:02.930
And when your father had another

00:02:02.930 --> 00:02:05.510
child with his new wife, a boy no

00:02:05.510 --> 00:02:08.400
less, you became even less important.

00:02:09.699 --> 00:02:11.740
This was the situation that

00:02:11.750 --> 00:02:13.560
young Elizabeth found herself in.

00:02:14.230 --> 00:02:17.510
A broken home is perhaps even a euphemism

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:19.983
for the early years of Elizabeth I.

00:02:21.509 --> 00:02:23.880
