00:02:24.070 --> 00:02:25.820
little chance of ever sitting

00:02:26.030 --> 00:02:27.979
on the throne, she was still the

00:02:27.980 --> 00:02:30.850
king’s daughter and had an extremely

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:33.300
privileged childhood and education.

00:02:34.110 --> 00:02:36.520
