00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:39.139
rhetoric, and music, and was

00:02:39.139 --> 00:02:40.890
fluent in five languages.

00:02:42.059 --> 00:02:44.660
From an early age, it was clear that

00:02:44.670 --> 00:02:47.416
this young girl was a cut above the

00:02:47.416 --> 00:02:49.240
rest, she was something special.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.210
She was tall, she had bright red

00:02:52.210 --> 00:02:54.890
hair, and was exceptionally clever.

00:02:56.160 --> 00:02:59.030
