00:03:01.880 --> 00:03:04.590
constantly on guard, looking out for

00:03:04.590 --> 00:03:07.330
men plotting and conspiring against her.

00:03:09.030 --> 00:03:11.690
This all started from a young age.

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:14.200
