00:03:28.456 --> 00:03:31.396
the hands of elder noblemen and officials.

00:03:32.546 --> 00:03:35.356
And, as you might imagine, before

00:03:35.406 --> 00:03:38.096
Henry had even taken his last breath,

00:03:38.426 --> 00:03:41.116
there were plenty of plots and schemes

00:03:41.286 --> 00:03:43.716
about how to manipulate and control

00:03:44.186 --> 00:03:46.426
not only his son and heir, but his

00:03:46.476 --> 00:03:48.986
other children, Mary and Elizabeth.

00:03:50.396 --> 00:03:52.776
At this point, the young Elizabeth

00:03:52.926 --> 00:03:54.786
was sent to live with Henry’s 6th

00:03:54.996 --> 00:03:57.086
and final wife, Catherine Parr,

00:03:57.296 --> 00:03:59.346
who had married a man called Thomas

00:03:59.386 --> 00:04:01.296
Seymour after Henry had died.

00:04:02.486 --> 00:04:05.076
If the surname “Seymour” rings a

00:04:05.076 --> 00:04:08.506
bell, Thomas Seymour’s sister was Jane

00:04:08.506 --> 00:04:11.316
Seymour, who was Henry VIII’s third wife.

