00:05:13.866 --> 00:05:16.066
dress to pieces to humiliate her.

00:05:17.246 --> 00:05:19.206
It was not until Catherine found

00:05:19.216 --> 00:05:21.696
Elizabeth in Seymour’s arms that she

00:05:21.706 --> 00:05:23.916
reacted and sent the young girl away

00:05:23.916 --> 00:05:26.066
from her palace never to see her again.

00:05:27.182 --> 00:05:29.519
Around a year after Elizabeth had been

00:05:29.519 --> 00:05:32.929
sent away, Catherine died, leaving all

00:05:32.929 --> 00:05:36.149
her riches to Seymour and making him one

00:05:36.149 --> 00:05:38.039
of the wealthiest men in the country.

00:05:39.039 --> 00:05:42.329
So, to recap, Henry VIII dies, his

00:05:42.489 --> 00:05:45.239
surviving wife, Catherine, marries this

00:05:45.299 --> 00:05:47.819
horrible abusive man, Thomas Seymour,

00:05:48.009 --> 00:05:50.279
who is planning to marry Elizabeth.

00:05:51.159 --> 00:05:53.569
Then Catherine dies, leaving her

00:05:53.569 --> 00:05:55.699
fortune to evil Thomas Seymour.

00:05:56.999 --> 00:05:59.429
Seymour now has the chance to carry out

00:05:59.459 --> 00:06:01.769
his plan to marry Elizabeth and gain

00:06:01.779 --> 00:06:04.429
influence over his nephew, Elizabeth’s

00:06:04.549 --> 00:06:07.159
