00:06:17.859 --> 00:06:18.849
have the chance to do it.

00:06:19.689 --> 00:06:22.579
He was arrested for treason, by his own

00:06:22.589 --> 00:06:25.529
brother no less, and eventually executed.

00:06:26.939 --> 00:06:29.429
Anyone involved with Seymour also

00:06:29.469 --> 00:06:31.619
came under suspicion, and this,

00:06:31.909 --> 00:06:33.689
naturally included Elizabeth.

00:06:34.229 --> 00:06:36.519
She was central to Seymour’s plan,

00:06:36.879 --> 00:06:38.849
even though there is no evidence that

00:06:38.849 --> 00:06:40.419
she wanted anything to do with him.

